# AGENTS.md — local-only / air-gapped project

## Constraints
- No cloud LLM APIs. Use only local Ollama/LM Studio endpoints.
- No code or logs leave the perimeter.

## Allowed models
- Qwen2.5-Coder-32B-Instruct q4_K_M
- Llama 3.1 8B Instruct q4_K_M

## Security
- Transcripts stored in `~/.local/ai-transcripts/`, never in repo.
- MCP servers only from internal registry.
